&gt; probably want a single bucket called New York. Instead, you should
&gt; have a text field for full text searches, and an unanalyzed keyword
&gt; field with doc_values enabled for aggregations

You need to create a subfield called keyword with type [keyword](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/keyword.html), which stores entire text as a single token.

